Integrity Statement

Description

It is a web-enabled bank statement designed to give credibility to customers of the Bank who wish to send bank statements to various embassies in the country as part of their visa application process.

Benefits

  • Comfort of knowing that the bank authenticates your statement
  • Gives customer credibility
